metadata.name: Transformation
metadata.description: With the development of biotechnology and the transmission, integration, conduction and combination of DNA coding, the secrets of the human brain are gradually being discovered. The mechanics of the human brain are connected to the mechanics of technology, such as the encoding of a computer chip. This also represents the relationship between biology and machines in cyber feminism, and the creation of social reality or fictional creation and how women re-code themselves in todayâ€™s era are questions that need to be considered.
